    "name": "Golden Holiday Hotel Nha Trang",
    "detail": "Just 1 night here by I assure my comment would be similar to everyone having stayed in this hotel. The hotel was well-built with eco-friendly structure, taking advantage of green trees and spaces from the first floor to the ceiling. It is very rare to see such a nice 3-star hotel like this, not only in Nha Trang but also in other provinces/cities of Vietnam. The staff are friendly. The room was superbly clean and new with wooden interior. The toilet was generally good but a little small. The floor could have been cleaner but that is everything you can complain. ",
